  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"EVEN IF YOU WERE EATEN, YOU HAVE TWO CHOICES...\"</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614960/extras/656a1c71d5d3801d1fb085b83f17edbc.avif?t=1668974784\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br>How often did you Wake up in a dark room, with no idea where you are or what to do next?<br>Two or three times?..<br>Well, not exactly more than ten times!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614960/extras/459b8f7b3f74a05d4a0ac32c7265ce70.avif?t=1668974784\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br>In this game, nobody tells you what to do – after all, it's simple: <br>- Do not touch sharp objects<br>- Beware of strange creatures<br>- Don't go in the dark<br>For a start it's enough.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614960/extras/42cf9d58f5cb30a3cc7b3ed56fbc882b.avif?t=1668974784\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br>But to solve this puzzle you'll need something more than perseverance and reaction. <br>More than observation and caution. <br>More than determination and luck...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614960/extras/11e10be0e2d7b29ac6dfe45c00a47ef1.avif?t=1668974784\" width=600 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to Neonomicon!</strong></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>\"EVEN IF YOU WERE EATEN, YOU HAVE TWO CHOICES...\"</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614960/extras/656a1c71d5d3801d1fb085b83f17edbc.avif?t=1668974784\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br>How often did you Wake up in a dark room, with no idea where you are or what to do next?<br>Two or three times?..<br>Well, not exactly more than ten times!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614960/extras/459b8f7b3f74a05d4a0ac32c7265ce70.avif?t=1668974784\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br>In this game, nobody tells you what to do – after all, it's simple: <br>- Do not touch sharp objects<br>- Beware of strange creatures<br>- Don't go in the dark<br>For a start it's enough.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614960/extras/42cf9d58f5cb30a3cc7b3ed56fbc882b.avif?t=1668974784\" width=600 height=128 /></span><br>But to solve this puzzle you'll need something more than perseverance and reaction. <br>More than observation and caution. <br>More than determination and luck...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/614960/extras/11e10be0e2d7b29ac6dfe45c00a47ef1.avif?t=1668974784\" width=600 height=128 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to Neonomicon!</strong></h2>",
